Ingest a Dataset

Source: R/ingest.R
ingest_dataset.Rd

High-level function to ingest a dataset into the database.

Usage

ingest_dataset(
  con,
  provider,
  dataset,
  dir_data,
  schema = "public",
  dir_googledata = NULL,
  email = NULL,
  overwrite = FALSE
)

Arguments

con

Database connection

provider

Data provider name

dataset

Dataset name

dir_data

Base directory for data

schema

Database schema

dir_googledata

Google Drive folder URL (optional)

email

Google Drive authentication email (optional)

overwrite

Whether to overwrite existing tables

Value

List with ingestion results and statistics

Examples

if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
result <- ingest_dataset(
  con = db_connection,
  provider = "swfsc.noaa.gov",
  dataset = "calcofi-db",
  dir_data = "/path/to/data",
  schema = "public"
)
} # }
